Package: ogrdbstats
Type: Package
Title: Analysis of Adaptive Immune Receptor Repertoire Genotype Statistics
Version: 0.5.0
Author: William Lees
Maintainer: William Lees <william@lees.org.uk>
Description: Multiple tools are now available for inferring the personalised 
    genotype from an AIRR-seq repertoire. Ogrdbstats can read the output from 
    a number of these tools, converting to a standard format and supplementing 
    with  rich data such as usage and characterisation of 'novel' germline 
    alleles. These reports can be particularly useful when considering the 
    validity of novel inferences. 
